author: The Current
description:
Watch and listen to Laufey's solo performance of "Promise"
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Icelandic artist Laufey released her third album, "A Matter of Time," on August 22, 2025. Back in 2023, Laufey visited The Current to perform a couple of solo renditions of songs from her second album, "Bewitched." Watch Laufey's performance of "Promise," above — a song, incidentally, that Laufey cowrote with Minnesota-born singer-songwriter Dan Wilson.  

All of Laufey's albums, 2022's "Everything I Know About Love," 2023's "Bewitched" and 2025's "A Matter of Time," are available on @AWAL. Song "Promise" co-written by Laufey and @danwilson. 

Musician
Laufey – piano and vocals

Credits
Guest – @laufey 
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Video Director – Josh Sauvageau
Camera Operators – Josh Sauvageau, Micah Kopecky
Audio – Eric Xu Romani
Graphics – Natalia Toledo
Digital Producer – Luke Taylor

Subscribe to our channel:
http://www.youtube.com/user/893TheC
title: Watch Laufey's piano-and-microphone performance of "Promise" at The Current #piano #shorts
